Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.54,0:23:56.29,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,This game is really hard for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.29,0:23:58.83,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,But if I can't finish it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.21,0:24:05.80,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,I p-probably won't be able to go on an \Nadventure with Hizutome-kun... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.22,0:24:10.68,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,Listen, I think you get good \Nat games impressively quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:15.73,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,but instead of these niche games, you might \Nwant to play one with broader appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.73,0:24:17.81,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:21.81,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,It's Hizutome's skill levels \Nthat make him such a frea—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.81,0:24:24.61,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,er, such a unique individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.61,0:24:27.74,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,I understand that you don't \Nwant to hold him back,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.74,0:24:30.53,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,but maybe you should work \Non your fundamentals.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.91,0:24:32.99,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,Fundamentals?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.99,0:24:38.12,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,The truth is, there's a game that unique \Nindividual will definitely try out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.12,0:24:39.08,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.75,0:24:42.63,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,The polar opposite of the \Ntrash games. The god game!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.63,0:24:47.92,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,With over 30 million players \Nworldwide, it's {\i1}Shangri-La Frontier{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.22,0:24:50.09,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,{\i1}SLF{\i0} for short, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.55,0:24:51.76,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.76,0:24:53.60,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,My sister's really into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.43,0:24:56.93,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,What if you have your \Nsister teach you the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.93,0:25:00.60,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,and become strong enough that you \Ncan show Hizutome-kun the ropes?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.06,0:25:02.06,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,Show him the ropes?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.06,0:25:05.44,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,Th-That's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.44,0:25:07.32,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.99,0:25:15.79,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,I'm going to become strong enough \Nto show Hizutome-kun the ropes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.33,0:25:17.95,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,{\i1}What Mana didn't realize
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.95,0:25:20.67,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,{\i1}was that her advice, offered \Nin a spirit of friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.67,0:25:25.80,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,{\i1}would create a hopeless \Naddict in {\i0}SLF{\i1}'s world.
